    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone looking for value over perfection. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though the car would benefit from a standard tune-up and some minor suspension work in the near future. Visually, the exterior shows some noticeable scratches and minor dings, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and floor mats. All essential electronics and safety features are functional, making this a practical choice for a buyer who appreciates a car with some history and character.",
