      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, a vehicle that epitomizes automotive excellence and meticulous stewardship. This unit remains in showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original luster and integrity. Every mechanical component has been maintained to exacting standards, ensuring a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning professional to acquire a vehicle of peerless quality and provenance.",
