    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s like stepping back in time\u2014this car is in such incredible shape, it practically looks like it just left the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without that brand new price tag, you\u2019ve gotta come check this out. I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I've loved it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
