    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis is impeccably maintained with documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. Performance is sharpened by a factory-spec M-variable limited-slip differential and perfectly calibrated MacPherson struts. Inside, the Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear, while the mechanical integrity is verified by a meticulous service history. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
