    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and it shows. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with a mirror-like finish, free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings; it has been protected with a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition. The premium leather seats are supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma, having never been smoked in or exposed to pets. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, binder-organized service history documenting every oil change and preventative maintenance milestone. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather driving. This sale includes both original master keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. If you are looking for a flawless example that requires zero investment, this is the one.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
