      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in showroom condition. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically pristine, it offers a driving experience that is indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle of true distinction.",
