      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and pampered like a member of the family. Seriously, it\u2019s in pristine condition\u2014not a scratch or a smudge to be found! It drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
