      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically superlative, boasting a documented VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term valvetrain and bottom-end reliability. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with factory crispness, delivering power through a reinforced rear subframe to an M-variable differential. The suspension kinematics remain stock and tight, with no bushing deflection or subframe hairline fractures. Finished in flawless Carbon Black, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A rare, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
